	<div style="text-align:right;">
		LAPA, Jenifer Elizabeth Figueiredo<sup>1</sup>; BRUNETTI, Marcia Elizabeth<sup>2</sup>		<BR>
		PIBITI		- Bolsa PUCPR-PIBITI		<BR>
